data.title: AMS :: Fellows Citations Archive
data.text:
Fellows of the American Mathematical Society Citations Archive

After the inaugural class of Fellows of the AMS and until 2023 the election and listing of Fellows were accompanied by citations. This archive includes the names, institutions, and citations as listed during this time period.

The list of Fellows of the AMS appears below. The institution listed has been designated by the individual. See the main Fellows of the AMS page for further information. You may also view this list as a table sorted by institution or you may view the list of 2023 Fellows and previous classes.

An asterisk to the right of a Fellow's name indicates that the individual is deceased.
